  "text": "According to the previous research, SFRP5 plays an anti-inflammatory role in metabolic homeostasis [CITATION_1] [CITATION_2] . However, to date, little is known about the effect of SFRP5 on NASH. The current study is aimed to investigate the efficacy of recombinant SFRP5 for intrahepatic inflammation of NASH.",
